      "isDeleted": false,
      "seed": 1625641529,
      "text": "❶ 配置 .claude/settings.json\n\n  hooks: { SessionStart: [{\n    command: \"echo '...'\n      >> $CLAUDE_ENV_FILE\"\n  }]}\n\n❷ 自动在每个命令前生效\n\n───────────────────────\n✓ 项目级别配置\n✓ 可版本控制\n✓ 团队共享友好",
      "fontSize": 10.917317107755746,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 15,
      "containerId": null,
