      "locked": false,
      "versionNonce": 1621998967,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "seed": 135457111,
      "text": "自动内存目录：\n~/.claude/projects/<proj>/memory/\n\nMEMORY.md 每次仅加载前 200 行\n详细内容按需读取\n\nClaude 递归查找：\n从当前目录向上查找\nCLAUDE.md / CLAUDE.local.md\n\n子目录内 CLAUDE.md 为按需加载",
      "fontSize": 11.337318366467562,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 188,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "自动内存目录：\n~/.claude/projects/<proj>/memory/\n\nMEMORY.md 每次仅加载前 200 行\n详细内容按需读取\n\nClaude 递归查找：\n从当前目录向上查找\nCLAUDE.md / CLAUDE.local.md\n\n子目录内 CLAUDE.md 为按需加载",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "version": 415,
      "index": "b5l",
      "autoResize": true
    },
